"async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Julien-Baker-Torres.-Credit-Ebru-Yildiz.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Julien-Baker-Torres.-Credit-Ebru-Yildiz-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Julien-Baker-Torres.-Credit-Ebru-Yildiz-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Julien-Baker-Torres.-Credit-Ebru-Yildiz-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Julien-Baker-Torres.-Credit-Ebru-Yildiz-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Julien-Baker-Torres.-Credit-Ebru-Yildiz-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/Julien-Baker">朱利安·贝克（Julien Baker）</a>和<a href="/artists/Torres">托雷斯（Torres）</a>宣布了他们的首张合作专辑“ send a prailer my way”，并分享了他们的歌曲“西尔维亚”（Sylvia）。在下面听。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/boygenius-the-record-nme-album-of-the-year-2023-3555857"><b>Boygenius关于“记录”的持久力量：“我们感觉就像我们希望的一样好”</b></a></li></ul><p>当贝克和托雷斯渴望唱歌时，柔软的曲目具有密封钢吉他，打击鼓和光滑的和声：“<em>西尔维亚 /别忘了我 / sylvia /觉得我错过了一切</em>，”描述了害怕让某人亲爱的他们亲爱的人看不见他们。</p><p> “西尔维亚”（Sylvia）伴随着黑白视频，看到两个在工作室里工作，并在演出中现场表演这首歌。贝克的<a href="/artists/Boygenius">Boygenius</a>乐队成员<a href="/artists/Lucy-Dacus">露西·达科斯（Lucy Dacus</a> ）在视觉效果中表现出一个客串。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Julien Baker＆Torres-“ Sylvia”（官方音乐视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/P0MhFvH-eTU?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>托雷斯在新闻稿中谈到这首歌时说<a href="/artists/Dolly-Parton">：</a> “早上，我去上北部庇护所的狗西尔维亚（Sylvia在。我哭了起来，感觉就像宇宙在告诉我她要成为我的（西尔维亚只是一个寄养）。</p><p> “我记得我想写这样的歌曲，这首歌在打开广播的五秒钟内可以在胸口感觉到这首歌，因为任何曾经有过与心爱的宠物分享房屋的人知道宠物是一家人 - 他们是你有史以来最好的朋友。”</p><p> “ Sylvia”跟随二人组发行的首张曲目“ The Tank In Tank”，这使Baker＆Torres <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/julien-baker-torres-share-country-inspired-debut-single-sugar-in-the-tank-3821988">在<em>吉米·法伦（Jimmy Fallon）主演</em>的<em>《今晚秀》</em>中露面，使歌迷感到惊讶</a>。</p><p>这两首歌都将在即将发行的首张合作专辑“ Send A Ala My Way”上展出。</p><p>该唱片定于4月18日通过Matador发行，自2016年贝克和托雷斯在芝加哥的林肯中心一起演出以来。演出结束时，一位歌手转向另一个，说：“你知道，我们应该制作一张乡村专辑。” </p><figure id="attachment_3832907" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3832907" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3832907" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Julien-Baker-Torres-Send-A-Prayer-My-Way-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1.jpg" alt="朱利安·贝克（Julien Baker）和托雷斯（Torres）的“向我的方式祈祷”专辑插图。信用：出版" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Julien-Baker-Torres-Send-A-Prayer-My-Way-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Julien-Baker-Torres-Send-A-Prayer-My-Way-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Julien-Baker-Torres-Send-A-Prayer-My-Way-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Julien-Baker-Torres-Send-A-Prayer-My-Way-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Julien-Baker-Torres-Send-A-Prayer-My-Way-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Julien-Baker-Torres-Send-A-Prayer-My-Way-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Julien-Baker-Torres-Send-A-Prayer-My-Way-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3832907" class="wp-caption-text">朱利安·贝克（Julien Baker）和托雷斯（Torres）的“向我的方式祈祷”专辑插图。信用：出版</figcaption></figure><p><em><a href="https://www.waterstones.com/book/valentine/elizabeth-wetmore/9780008331962" target="_blank" rel="noopener">瓦伦丁（Valentine）</a></em>的作者伊丽莎白·韦特莫尔（Elizabeth Wetmore）将“祈祷我的方式”描述为“一张该死的乡村专辑，以最佳的传统传统写作和演唱 - 偏见，颠覆性，工人阶级，并决心不仅要与成瘾，成瘾，成瘾搏斗遗憾和错误的决定，也有压迫性的权力制度。”</p><p>她继续说：“这些歌曲是关于将漫长的转变和疲倦的骨头疲倦，希望有一点杂草和一个安静的地方来抬起脚的歌曲。或者再次从货车上掉下来，想知道这一次是否会终于将您拖到车轮下；或认为错误的决定是您知道如何做出的唯一决定。”</p><p>您可以<a href="https://matadorrecords.com/products/ole2108-send-a-prayer-my-way" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>预订和预示为“发送祈祷”。</p><p>在其他地方，贝克此前在10月5日<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/julien-baker-announces-new-york-city-residency-at-webster-hall-3783426">在纽约的韦伯斯特音乐厅（NYC Webster Hall）进行了为期三晚的比赛</a>，在那里她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/julien-baker-ends-new-york-gig-early-due-to-illness-confirms-new-date-with-special-guest-3800501">与托雷斯（Torres）首次亮相了两首新歌</a>。然而，她生病后第二天晚上被迫离开舞台中期，乐队成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lucy-dacus">露西·达科斯（Lucy Dacus）</a>被迫宣布演出将过早结束。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-julien-baker-debut-two-new-songs-in-chicago-3797594">贝克还曾在芝加哥首次亮相两首新曲目</a>- “中间儿童”和“地下室高处”。在其他地方，她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-julien-baker-bring-out-bartees-strange-for-ringside-in-washington-dc-3798053">还与华盛顿特区的Bartees Strange一起参加了“马戏团”的特别演绎</a>。</p><p>去年，她与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/boygenius">Boygenuis</a>团聚，获得了首张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/boygenius-the-record-review-the-instant-classic-we-were-hoping-for-3419059">《 The Record》</a> ，该专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/boygenius-julien-baker-2024-grammys-music-language-family-3582158">获得了三项格莱美奖。</a> “唱片”是<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/boygenius-the-record-nme-album-of-the-year-2023-3555857">2023年的<i>NME</i>年度最佳专辑</a>，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/boygenius-the-record-review-the-instant-classic-we-were-hoping-for-3419059">在<i>NME</i>上获得了五星级评论</a>，埃里卡·坎贝尔（Erica Campbell）写道：“这次首次亮相是当您完全可以看到自己时会发生什么的出色证明。</p><p> “尽管专辑的12首曲目中的每条曲目都可以很好地适合他们的个人唱片之一，但他们的工作共同存在着更明亮的大胆存在，使他们能够同时单独点亮。”</p><p>与此同时，贝克和托雷斯对国家类型的填海遵循<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chappell-roan">查佩尔·罗恩（Chappell Roan）</a>进行了类似的行动，他在《星期六夜现场》上首次亮相了一条新的“女同性恋国歌”乡村曲目“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-debuts-new-lesbian-anthem-country-song-on-snl-3809048">The Giver</a> ” <a href="https://www.nme.com/series/saturday-night-live"><em>。</em></a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/julien-baker-torres-share-yearnful-single-sylvia-and-announce-debut-collab-album-send-a-prayer-my-way-3832889">朱利安·贝克（Julien Baker）和托雷斯（Torres）的邮报分享了渴望的新单曲“西尔维亚（Sylvia）”，并宣布首张合作专辑“ Send a a prailer my Way”</a>出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
杰森·施瓦茨曼（Jason Schwartzman）返回13年来首次新音乐的椰子唱片https://www.nme.com/news/music/jason-schwartzman-returning-as-coconut-records-for-forst-new-music-in-13 are-13 Yare-3832875？ Schwartzman-As-As-As-Coconut-Records for Fort-New Music-13年Tom SkinnerWed, 29 Jan 2025 14:29:06 +0000 Film NewsMusic NewsNewsIndie https://www.nme.com/?p=3832875 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/JasonSchwartzman-Coconut-Records-new-music.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="杰森·施瓦茨曼（Jason Schwartzman）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/JasonSchwartzman-Coconut-Records-new-music.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/JasonSchwartzman-Coconut-Records-new-music-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/JasonSchwartzman-Coconut-Records-new-music-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/JasonSchwartzman-Coconut-Records-new-music-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/JasonSchwartzman-Coconut-Records-new-music-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/JasonSchwartzman-Coconut-Records-new-music-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>最近的视频预告片透露他正在“在FaceTime上写[一本新的椰子记录”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jason-schwartzman-returning-as-coconut-records-for-first-new-music-in-13-years-3832875">杰森·施瓦茨曼（Jason Schwartzman）的帖子返回了13年来首次新音乐的椰子唱片，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/JasonSchwartzman-Coconut-Records-new-music.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="杰森·施瓦茨曼（Jason Schwartzman）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/JasonSchwartzman-Coconut-Records-new-music.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/JasonSchwartzman-Coconut-Records-new-music-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/JasonSchwartzman-Coconut-Records-new-music-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/JasonSchwartzman-Coconut-Records-new-music-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/JasonSchwartzman-Coconut-Records-new-music-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/JasonSchwartzman-Coconut-Records-new-music-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>杰森·施瓦茨曼（Jason Schwartzman）将在13年内以椰子唱片的形式返回他的第一场新音乐。</p><p>这位美国演员和音乐家曾出演过众多韦斯·安德森（Wes Anderson）的电影，在《绰号：nighttiming》（2007年）和“戴维（Davy）”（2009年）下发行了两张录音室专辑。施瓦茨曼（Schwartzman）的独立个人项目还为2012年喜剧剧院<em>山羊</em>提供了分数。</p><p>上个月，施瓦茨曼（Schwartzman）的朋友兼合作者本·克威尔（Ben Kweller）证实，椰子唱片在他即将发行的新唱片“掩护镜子”上为“抑郁症”做出了贡献。</p><p> Schwartzman随后在<a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@coconutrecordsofficial" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Tiktok</a>上推出了官方的椰子唱片资料，在那里他分享了一系列由他的旧音乐配乐的视频。第一个剪辑伴随着标签“ #coconutrecords #jasonschwartzman #benkweller #nostalgiacore”。</p><p>下一个视频显示Schwartzman和Kweller“在FaceTime上写[A]新的椰子记录”，标题包括标签“ #NewalBum，#NewMusic和#SongWritingProcess”。 </p><blockquote class="tiktok-embed" cite="https://www.tiktok.com/@coconutrecordsofficial/video/7464368424542670111" data-video-id="7464368424542670111" data-embed-from="oembed" style="max-width:605px; min-width:325px;"><section> <a target="_blank" title="@coconutrecordsofficial" href="https://www.tiktok.com/@coconutrecordsofficial?refer=embed">@coconutrecordsofficial</a></p><p>在<a title="新型" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/newmusic?refer=embed">FaceTime</a><a title="Benkweller" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/benkweller?refer=embed">上</a><a title="合作" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/collaboration?refer=embed">编写</a>新的椰子记录，就像<a title="newalbum" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/newalbum?refer=embed">#NewalBum</a> <a title="那样" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/ThatsWhatILike?refer=embed">#ThatSwhatilike</a> <a title="这个" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/thisorthat?refer=embed">#thisorthat</a> <a title="SongwritingProcess" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/songwritingprocess?refer=embed">#songwritingprocess</a> <a title="歌曲创作" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/songwriting?refer=embed">#songwriting</a> <a title="歌曲撰写的提示" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/songwritingtips?refer=embed">#songwritingtips</a> <a title="椰子记录" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/coconutrecords?refer=embed">#coconutrecords</a> <a title="Jasonschwartzman" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/jasonschwartzman?refer=embed">#jasonschwartzman</a></p><p> <a target="_blank" title="♬不是你是我 - 椰子记录" href="https://www.tiktok.com/music/It's-Not-You-It's-Me-7343769088281905154?refer=embed">♬不是你是我 - 椰子记录</a></section></blockquote><p><script async src="https://www.tiktok.com/embed.js"></script></p><p> 后来上传的“公共服务公告”字幕，在录音室中显示了这对夫妇的静止图像。</p><p> “我和我的朋友本正在写作和录音，我们了解到，如果我们有1000个追随者，我们将能够在tiktok上直播，所以请告诉您的朋友，以便我们在制作Jamz时可以打开CAMZ，”屏幕上的消息读。</p><p>在最近的剪辑中，Schwartzman在录制键盘部分的工作中可以看到。您可以在此处查看视频： </p><blockquote class="tiktok-embed" cite="https://www.tiktok.com/@coconutrecordsofficial/video/7464431726845005098" data-video-id="7464431726845005098" data-embed-from="oembed" style="max-width:605px; min-width:325px;"><section> <a target="_blank" title="@coconutrecordsofficial" href="https://www.tiktok.com/@coconutrecordsofficial?refer=embed">@coconutrecordsofficial</a></p><p>公共服务公告<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f618.png" alt="😘" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a title="椰子记录" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/coconutrecords?refer=embed">#coconutrecords</a> <a title="Jasonschwartzman" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/jasonschwartzman?refer=embed">#jasonschwartzman</a> <a title="Benkweller" target="_blank" href="htt